lso making a statement these days with their sturdy leaves, bright colors and unique textures and shapes. They just look different than other flowers.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-22019 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/This-ultimate-guide-will-teach-you-all-about-using-succulents-for-wedding-bouquets-and-boutonnieres.jpg\" alt=\"This ultimate guide will teach you all about using succulents for wedding bouquets and boutonnieres!\" width=\"735\" height=\"1102\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/This-ultimate-guide-will-teach-you-all-about-using-succulents-for-wedding-bouquets-and-boutonnieres-53x80.jpg 53w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/This-ultimate-guide-will-teach-you-all-about-using-succulents-for-wedding-bouquets-and-boutonnieres-200x300.jpg 200w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/This-ultimate-guide-will-teach-you-all-about-using-succulents-for-wedding-bouquets-and-boutonnieres-250x375.jpg 250w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/This-ultimate-guide-will-teach-you-all-about-using-succulents-for-wedding-bouquets-and-boutonnieres-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/This-ultimate-guide-will-teach-you-all-about-using-succulents-for-wedding-bouquets-and-boutonnieres-500x750.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/This-ultimate-guide-will-teach-you-all-about-using-succulents-for-wedding-bouquets-and-boutonnieres-585x877.jpg 585w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/This-ultimate-guide-will-teach-you-all-about-using-succulents-for-wedding-bouquets-and-boutonnieres-600x900.jpg 600w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/This-ultimate-guide-will-teach-you-all-about-using-succulen