 few different options for succulent bouquets. You can get one for the bride and smaller ones for bridesmaids or mothers.<\/p>\n<p>There are also several vendors on <a href=\"http:\/\/www.awin1.com\/cread.php?awinaffid=233213&awinmid=6220&clickref=weddingguide_succulentbouquet&p=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.etsy.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Dsucculent%2Bwedding%2Bbouquet%26ref%3Dguided_search_2_1%26as_prefix%3Dsucculent%2Bbo%26explicit%3D1%26guided_search%3D1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">Etsy<\/a> who create beautiful bouquets.<\/p>\n<p>Make sure you order several months in advance to ensure the artist has openings and can ensure your bouquet is delivered in time for your special day.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-21837 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-succulents-in-this-wedding-bouquet-really-stand-out.jpg\" alt=\"The succulents in this wedding bouquet really stand out!\" width=\"735\" height=\"1103\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-succulents-in-this-wedding-bouquet-really-stand-out-53x80.jpg 53w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-succulents-in-this-wedding-bouquet-really-stand-out-200x300.jpg 200w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-succulents-in-this-wedding-bouquet-really-stand-out-250x375.jpg 250w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-succulents-in-this-wedding-bouquet-really-stand-out-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-succulents-in-this-wedding-bouquet-really-stand-out-500x750.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-succulents-in-this-wedding-bouquet-really-stand-out-585x878.jpg 585w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-succulents-in-this-wedding-bouquet-really-stand-out-600x90