s are a great option. They are easy to make even if you haven\u2019t done anything like it before.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-21834 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-succulent-boutonniere-for-the-groom-looked-so-classy.jpg\" alt=\"The succulent boutonniere for the groom looked so classy\" width=\"735\" height=\"1103\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-succulent-boutonniere-for-the-groom-looked-so-classy-53x80.jpg 53w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-succulent-boutonniere-for-the-groom-looked-so-classy-200x300.jpg 200w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-succulent-boutonniere-for-the-groom-looked-so-classy-250x375.jpg 250w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-succulent-boutonniere-for-the-groom-looked-so-classy-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-succulent-boutonniere-for-the-groom-looked-so-classy-500x750.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-succulent-boutonniere-for-the-groom-looked-so-classy-585x878.jpg 585w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-succulent-boutonniere-for-the-groom-looked-so-classy-600x900.jpg 600w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-succulent-boutonniere-for-the-groom-looked-so-classy-700x1050.jpg 700w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-succulent-boutonniere-for-the-groom-looked-so-classy.jpg 735w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 735px) 100vw, 735px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>You can see a full written tutorial plus a video tutorial for how to make them by <a href=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/succulent-boutonniere-ideas-for-your-diy-wedding\/\">clicking here<\/a>. I also have a tutorial in my book, <a href=\"http:\/\/amzn.to\/2jvAIwP\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">Idiot\u2019s Guides: Succulents.<\/a><\/p>\n<p>The awesome thing about boutonnieres is you can easily make them all a little different! Since men aren\u2019t always keen on matching, this is a fun way to change things up a bit.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-21828 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/I-love-the-colors-in-this-succulent-boutonniere.jpg\" alt=\"I love the colors in this succulent boutonniere\" width=\"735\" height=\"1103\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/I-love-the-colors-in-this-succulent-boutonniere-53x80.jpg 53w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/I-love-the-colors-in-this-succulent-boutonniere-200x300.jpg 200w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/I-love-the-colors-in-this-succulent-boutonniere-250x375.jpg 250w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/I-love-the-colors-in-this-succulent-boutonniere-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/I-love-the-colors-in-this-succulent-boutonniere-500x750.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/I-love-the-colors-in-this-succulent-boutonniere-585x878.jpg 585w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/I-love-the-colors-in-this-succulent-boutonniere-600x900.jpg 600w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/I-love-the-colors-in-this-succulent-boutonniere-700x1050.jpg 700w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/I-love-the-colors-in-this-succulent-boutonniere.jpg 735w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 735px) 100vw, 735px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Succulent cuttings from <a href=\"https:\/\/thesucculentsource.com\/collections\/succulent-cuttings\/?