background-size:cover;padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;\"><div class=\"fusion-menu-anchor\" id=\"corsage\"><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-5\"><h3>Succulent Corsages<\/h3>\n<p>The women also need some succulents for the wedding! There are a lot of different ways you can do the corsage, so have some fun with it!<\/p>\n<p>One of my favorite ways is to create a succulent cuff. Rather than create the wristlet with <a href=\"https:\/\/amzn.to\/2Qc4Jhx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">wire<\/a> or <a href=\"https:\/\/amzn.to\/2M4ik7l\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">ribbon<\/a>, simply <a href=\"https:\/\/amzn.to\/2iBz6zK\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">glue<\/a> succulents onto a <a href=\"https:\/\/amzn.to\/2M5c13m\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">decorative cuff<\/a>. This is a really simple approach and very quick and easy to do.<\/p>\n<p>Here are a few from The Succulent Source:<\/p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_22121\" style=\"width: 595px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-22121\" class=\"wp-image-22121 size-large\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/succulent-cuffs-for-a-wedding-party-585x754.jpg\" alt=\"succulent cuffs for a wedding party\" width=\"585\" height=\"754\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/succulent-cuffs-for-a-wedding-party-62x80.jpg 62w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/succulent-cuffs-for-a-wedding-party-200x258.jpg 200w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/succulent-cuffs-for-a-wedding-party-250x322.jpg 250w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/succulent-cuffs-for-a-wedding-party-400x516.jpg 400w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/succulent-cuffs-for-a-wedding-party-500x645.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunsh