 height=\"1103\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/You-can-make-your-own-succulent-wrist-corsage-with-ribbon-53x80.jpg 53w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/You-can-make-your-own-succulent-wrist-corsage-with-ribbon-200x300.jpg 200w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/You-can-make-your-own-succulent-wrist-corsage-with-ribbon-250x375.jpg 250w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/You-can-make-your-own-succulent-wrist-corsage-with-ribbon-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/You-can-make-your-own-succulent-wrist-corsage-with-ribbon-500x750.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/You-can-make-your-own-succulent-wrist-corsage-with-ribbon-585x878.jpg 585w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/You-can-make-your-own-succulent-wrist-corsage-with-ribbon-600x900.jpg 600w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/You-can-make-your-own-succulent-wrist-corsage-with-ribbon-700x1050.jpg 700w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/You-can-make-your-own-succulent-wrist-corsage-with-ribbon.jpg 735w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 735px) 100vw, 735px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>We got a few that were a <a href=\"http:\/\/www.awin1.com\/cread.php?awinaffid=233213&awinmid=6220&clickref=weddingguide_euccabracelet&p=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.etsy.com%2Flisting%2F291753007%2Fsucculent-bracelet-succulent-corsage%3Fref%3Dshop_home_active_3%26ep_click%3D1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">wire bracelet<\/a>, and the rest tied on with <a href=\"http:\/\/www.awin1.com\/cread.php?awinaffid=233213&awinmid=6220&clickref=weddingguide_euccabracelet&p=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.etsy.com%2Flisting%2F210037588%2Fsucculent-corsage-wildflower%3Fref%3Dshop_home_active_2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">ribbon<\/a>. While I liked the look of the ribbons with the corsage, the wedding party definitely preferred the bracelet option as they were easier to put on and didn\u2019t slip or need to be adjusted.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-21826 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-bridal-party-loved-the-succulent-wrist-corsages.jpg\" alt=\"The bridal party loved the succulent wrist corsages\" width=\"735\" height=\"1103\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-bridal-party-loved-the-succulent-wrist-corsages-53x80.jpg 53w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-bridal-party-loved-the-succulent-wrist-corsages-200x300.jpg 200w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-bridal-party-loved-the-succulent-wrist-corsages-250x375.jpg 250w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-bridal-party-loved-the-succulent-wrist-corsages-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-bridal-party-loved-the-succulent-wrist-corsages-500x750.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-bridal-party-loved-the-succulent-wrist-corsages-585x878.jpg 585w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-bridal-party-loved-the-succulent-wrist-corsages-600x900.jpg 600w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-bridal-party-loved-the-succulent-wrist-corsages-700x1050.jpg 700w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-bridal-party-loved-the-succulent-wrist-corsages.jpg 735w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 735px) 100vw, 735px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>A traditional succulent corsage like this is a little bit trickier to DIY than a boutonniere, but still a pretty simple project. You\u2019ll follow the same approach in creating the wire stem for the succulents, but wrap the wires together and form a circle, rather than bunching them all together.<\/p>\n<p>And of course, the succulent cuttings from <a href=\"https:\/\/mountaincrestgardens.com\/succulent-cuttings\/?aff=2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">Mountain Crest Gardens<\/a> or <a href=\"https:\/\/thesucculentsource.com\/collections\/succulent-cuttings\/?aff=20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">The Succulent Source<\/a> are great options if you want to take the DIY approach.<\/p>\n<p>Make sure to let your bridesmaids know they can take their corsage apart and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/succulent-bouquet-garden\/\">plant the succulents<\/a> when the wedding is over, just like with the bouquet. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/succulent-bouquet-garden\/\">Click here<\/a> to learn how.<\/p>\n<h3>Succulent Hair Pieces<\/h3>\n<p>A really unique way to use succulents for bridesmaids or even the bride, is by doing succulent hair pieces. Succulent artists make some really amazing <a href=\"http:\/\/www.awin1.com\/cread.php?awinaffid=233213&awinmid=6220&clickref=weddingguide_euccacomb&p=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.etsy.com%2Fshop%2FEucca%3Fref%3Dss_profile%26section_id%3D23131815\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">combs<\/a> and <a href=\"http:\/\/www.awin1.com\/cread.php?awinaffid=233213&awinmid=6220&clickref=weddingguide_euccacrown&p=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.etsy.com%2Fshop%2FEucca%3Fref%3Dss_profile%26section_id%3D16842911\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">crowns<\/a>.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_22125\" style=\"width: 580px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-22125\" class=\"wp-image-22125 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/succulent-crown-or-headband-by-eucca.jpg\" alt=\"succulent crown or headband by eucca\" width=\"570\" height=\"713\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/succulent-crown-or-headband-by-eucca-64x80.jpg 64w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/succulent-crown-or-headband-by-eucca-200x250.jpg 200w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/succulent-crown-or-headband-by-eucca-250x313.jpg 250w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/succulent-crown-or-headband-by-eucca-400x500.jpg 400w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/succulent-crown-or-headband-by-eucca-500x625.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/succulent-crown-or-headband-by-eucca.jpg 570w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 570px) 100vw, 570px\" \/><p id=\"caption-attachment-22125\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Image Source: <a href=\"http:\/\/www.awin1.com\/cread.php?awinaffid=233213&awinmid=6220&clickref=weddingguide_euccacomb&p=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.etsy.com%2Fshop%2FEucca%3Fref%3Dss_profile%26section_id%3D23131815\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">Eucca on Etsy<\/a><\/p><\/div>\n<p>If you are taking the DIY approach, it\u2019s easy enough to glue succulents to a <a href=\"https:\/\/amzn.to\/2wPjJtl\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">hair comb<\/a>, similar to what I did with my <a href=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/how-to-make-a-succulent-hat\/\">succulent hat<\/a>.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_22123\" style=\"width: 580px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-22123\" class=\"size-full wp-image-22123\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/eucca-succulent-floral-hair-piece.jpg\" alt=\"eucca succulent floral hair piece\" width=\"570\" height=\"710\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/eucca-succulent-floral-hair-piece-64x80.jpg 64w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/eucca-succulent-floral-hair-piece-200x249.jpg 200w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/eucca-succulent-floral-hair-piece-250x311.jpg 250w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/eucca-succulent-floral-hair-piece-400x498.jpg 400w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/eucca-succulent-floral-hair-piece-500x623.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/eucca-succulent-floral-hair-piece.jpg 570w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 570px) 100vw, 570px\" \/><p id=\"caption-attachment-22123\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Image Source: <a href=\"http:\/\/www.awin1.com\/cread.php?awinaffid=233213&awinmid=6220&clickref=weddingguide_euccacomb&p=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.etsy.com%2Fshop%2FEucca%3Fref%3Dss_profile%26section_id%3D23131815\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">Eucca on Etsy<\/a><\/p><\/div>\n<p>Or, you could use the same creation process as a boutonniere or corsage but make the whole thing longer and form it into a crown.<\/p>\n<p><div style=\"width: 639px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static1.squarespace.com\/static\/51945be4e4b05b135b14e8c4\/t\/520c906ee4b0bc18c9732a84\/1430836500223\/succulentcrown.JPG?format=1000w\" alt=\" diy succulent crown via needles + leaves \" width=\"629\" height=\"397\" \/><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Image Source: <a href=\"https:\/\/needlesandleaves.net\/blog\/2013\/8\/14\/diy-succulent-crown\" target=\"_blank\">Needles and Leaves<\/a><\/p><\/div>\n<div id=\"attachment_22124\" style=\"width: 574px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-22124\" class=\"wp-image-22124 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/succulent-crown-for-a-wedding-by-dalla-vita.jpg\" alt=\"succulent crown for a wedding by dalla vita\" width=\"564\" height=\"704\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/succulent-crown-for-a-wedding-by-dalla-vita-64x80.jpg 64w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/succulent-crown-for-a-wedding-by-dalla-vita-200x250.jpg 200w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/succulent-crown-for-a-wedding-by-dalla-vita-250x312.jpg 250w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/succulent-crown-for-a-wedding-by-dalla-vita-400x499.jpg 400w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/succulent-crown-for-a-wedding-by-dalla-vita-500x624.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/succulent-crown-for-a-wedding-by-dalla-vita.jpg 564w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 564px) 100vw, 564px\" \/><p id=\"caption-attachment-22124\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Image Source: <a href=\"http:\/\/dallavita.com\/\" target=\"_blank\">Dalla Vita<\/a><\/p><\/div><\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-clearfix\"><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div id=\"centerpiece\"><div class=\"fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-6 nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 0px;border-color:#eae9e9;border-style:solid;\" ><div class=\"fusion-builder-row fusion-row\"><div class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-5 fusion_builder_column_1_1 1_1 fusion-one-full fusion-column-first fusion-column-last\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-flex-column-wrapper-legacy\" style=\"background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;\"><div class=\"fusion-menu-anchor\" id=\"centerpiece\"><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-6\"><h3>Succulent Wedding Centerpieces<\/h3>\n<p>There are so many creative ideas for incorporating succulents into your wedding centerpieces. And, as always, you can keep the succulents when you\u2019re done to have a reminder of this special day!<\/p>\n<p>A more formal approach to centerpieces is to use a potted arrangement. Simply plant succulents in pots that coordinate with the wedding colors, and voila!<\/p>\n<p>This is what we did for my sister-in-law, using terracotta pots to keep things more natural and less formal. They really helped tie all the tables together and we had lots of comments from guests about how pretty they were!<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-21836 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-succulent-table-arrangements-were-beautiful-at-the-wedding.jpg\" alt=\"The succulent table arrangements were beautiful at the wedding\" width=\"735\" height=\"1103\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-succulent-table-arrangements-were-beautiful-at-the-wedding-53x80.jpg 53w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-succulent-table-arrangements-were-beautiful-at-the-wedding-200x300.jpg 200w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-succulent-table-arrangements-were-beautiful-at-the-wedding-250x375.jpg 250w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-succulent-table-arrangements-were-beautiful-at-the-wedding-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-succulent-table-arrangements-were-beautiful-at-the-wedding-500x750.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-succulent-table-arrangements-were-beautiful-at-the-wedding-585x878.jpg 585w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-succulent-table-arrangements-were-beautiful-at-the-wedding-600x900.jpg 600w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-succulent-table-arrangements-were-beautiful-at-the-wedding-700x1050.jpg 700w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-succulent-table-arrangements-were-beautiful-at-the-wedding.jpg 735w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 735px) 100vw, 735px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>I also love the look of these <a href=\"https:\/\/lookingsharpcactus.com\/collections\/bottle-planters-gardens\" target=\"_blank\">wine bottle planters<\/a> from Looking Sharp Cactus. You can buy a <a href=\"https:\/\/lookingsharpcactus.com\/collections\/bottle-planters-gardens\/products\/glass-succulent-planter-wine-bottle-planter-garden-wine-gifts-house-warming-windowsill-planter-gift-ideas-for-mom-indoor-plants\" target=\"_blank\">DIY kit<\/a> or <a href=\"https:\/\/lookingsharpcactus.com\/collections\/bottle-planters-gardens\/products\/wine-bottle-planter-wine-gifts-wine-bottle-decor-indoor-plants-succulent-glass-terrarium-indoor-herb-garden-alcohol-gifts-glass?variant=7042478997527\" target=\"_blank\">just the planter<\/a> (and use plants you already have).<\/p>\n<p>If the wedding theme is a little more organic, you can simply set succulents on the table with rocks, logs, crystals, candles, or whatever else you come up with! <a href=\"http:\/\/amzn.to\/2jvAIwP\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">The Idiot\u2019s Guides: Succulents<\/a> has a tutorial on how to set this up, and you can find some other inspiration below.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_22127\" style=\"width: 610px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-22127\" class=\"wp-image-22127\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/martha-stewart-succulent-table-decor.jpg\" alt=\"martha stewart succulent table decor\" width=\"600\" height=\"750\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/martha-stewart-succulent-table-decor-64x80.jpg 64w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/martha-stewart-succulent-table-decor-200x250.jpg 200w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/martha-stewart-succulent-table-decor-250x313.jpg 250w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/martha-stewart-succulent-table-decor-400x500.jpg 400w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/martha-stewart-succulent-table-decor-500x625.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/martha-stewart-succulent-table-decor-585x731.jpg 585w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/martha-stewart-succulent-table-decor-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/martha-stewart-succulent-table-decor-700x875.jpg 700w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/martha-stewart-succulent-table-decor-768x960.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/martha-stewart-succulent-table-decor-800x1000.jpg 800w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/martha-stewart-succulent-table-decor.jpg 1040w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><p id=\"caption-attachment-22127\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Image Source: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.marthastewartweddings.com\/356064\/succulent-wedding-ideas?slide=742481\" target=\"_blank\">Martha Steward Weddings<\/a><\/p><\/div>\n<p>Naturally you\u2019ll want centerpieces for each of the tables where people will be sitting, but don\u2019t forget to use succulents for the guest book table too! You may even want a small arrangement or two on the food table.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-21843 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Using-succulents-at-the-guest-book-table-is-a-clever-idea.jpg\" alt=\"Using succulents at the guest book table is a clever idea\" width=\"735\" height=\"1103\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Using-succulents-at-the-guest-book-table-is-a-clever-idea-53x80.jpg 53w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Using-succulents-at-the-guest-book-table-is-a-clever-idea-200x300.jpg 200w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Using-succulents-at-the-guest-book-table-is-a-clever-idea-250x375.jpg 250w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Using-succulents-at-the-guest-book-table-is-a-clever-idea-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Using-succulents-at-the-guest-book-table-is-a-clever-idea-500x750.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Using-succulents-at-the-guest-book-table-is-a-clever-idea-585x878.jpg 585w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Using-succulents-at-the-guest-book-table-is-a-clever-idea-600x900.jpg 600w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Using-succulents-at-the-guest-book-table-is-a-clever-idea-700x1050.jpg 700w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Using-succulents-at-the-guest-book-table-is-a-clever-idea.jpg 735w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 735px) 100vw, 735px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>A great thing about succulent centerpieces is they can easily be given to parents, bridesmaids, or even your wedding planner as a thank you gift after the wedding. It\u2019s a great way to kill two birds with one stone while still giving a meaningful gift to those who helped with the occasion.<\/p>\n<p>For my sister-in-law\u2019s wedding, I made all the centerpieces beforehand using a <a href=\"https:\/\/mountaincrestgardens.com\/wholesale-assortments\/?aff=2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">wholesale flat of succulents<\/a> from Mountain Crest Gardens. For instructions on planting succulents <a href=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/how-to-plant-a-succulent\/\">click here<\/a>. Or <a href=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/tips-for-arranging-succulents-in-containers-and-landscapes\/\">click here<\/a> for tips on how to design the perfect arrangement.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-21832 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Succulents-and-airplants-made-beautiful-centerpieces.jpg\" alt=\"Succulents and airplants made beautiful centerpieces\" width=\"735\" height=\"1103\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Succulents-and-airplants-made-beautiful-centerpieces-53x80.jpg 53w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Succulents-and-airplants-made-beautiful-centerpieces-200x300.jpg 200w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Succulents-and-airplants-made-beautiful-centerpieces-250x375.jpg 250w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Succulents-and-airplants-made-beautiful-centerpieces-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Succulents-and-airplants-made-beautiful-centerpieces-500x750.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Succulents-and-airplants-made-beautiful-centerpieces-585x878.jpg 585w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Succulents-and-airplants-made-beautiful-centerpieces-600x900.jpg 600w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Succulents-and-airplants-made-beautiful-centerpieces-700x1050.jpg 700w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Succulents-and-airplants-made-beautiful-centerpieces.jpg 735w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 735px) 100vw, 735px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>You can also purchase completed arrangements too. There are several Etsy sellers with beautiful options including <a href=\"http:\/\/www.awin1.com\/cread.php?awinaffid=233213&awinmid=6220&clickref=weddingguide_succwonderland&p=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.etsy.com%2Fshop%2FSucculentWonderland%3Fref%3Dss_profile\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">Succulent Wonderland<\/a>, <a href=\"http:\/\/www.awin1.com\/cread.php?awinaffid=233213&awinmid=6220&clickref=weddingguide_succulentsalon&p=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.etsy.com%2Fshop%2FSucculentSalon%3Fref%3Dss_profile\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">Succulent Salon<\/a>, and <a href=\"http:\/\/www.awin1.com\/cread.php?awinaffid=233213&awinmid=6220&clickref=weddingguide_succulentartworks&p=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.etsy.com%2Fshop%2FSucculentArtWorks%3Fref%3Dss_profile\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">Succulent Art Works<\/a>.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-clearfix\"><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div id=\"favors\"><div class=\"fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-7 nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 0px;border-color:#eae9e9;border-style:solid;\" ><div class=\"fusion-builder-row fusion-row\"><div class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-6 fusion_builder_column_1_1 1_1 fusion-one-full fusion-column-first fusion-column-last\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-flex-column-wrapper-legacy\" style=\"background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;\"><div class=\"fusion-menu-anchor\" id=\"favors\"><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-7\"><h3>Succulent Wedding Favors<\/h3>\n<p>Clearly I\u2019m a fan of using succulents however you can for your wedding. But, if you really want to show your guests how much you love them, you\u2019ll definitely want to give succulent wedding favors.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/www.awin1.com\/cread.php?awinaffid=233213&awinmid=6220&clickref=wedding_letlovegrow&p=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.etsy.com%2Flisting%2F225138642%2Fset-of-25-let-love-grow-succulent-favor%3Fref%3Dshop_home_active_14\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"https:\/\/i.pinimg.com\/564x\/05\/10\/94\/05109414e6e617e92d9cf67d2d7eaffe.jpg\" alt=\"Let Love Grow Succulent Favor Tags, Wedding Favor tags\" width=\"564\" height=\"846\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>A lot of wedding favors have meaning for the bride and groom, but they go unused by the guests. Or, they are just little trinkets that are thrown away or forgotten after the big day.<\/p>\n<p>This is not the case with succulent wedding favors! These adorable little plants will be a source of conversation for your guests and will definitely make people happy and excited to take them home.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-21845 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/You-can-make-your-own-succulent-wedding-favors-for-your-guests-to-take-home.jpg\" alt=\"You can make your own succulent wedding favors for your guests to take home\" width=\"735\" height=\"1103\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/You-can-make-your-own-succulent-wedding-favors-for-your-guests-to-take-home-53x80.jpg 53w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/You-can-make-your-own-succulent-wedding-favors-for-your-guests-to-take-home-200x300.jpg 200w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/You-can-make-your-own-succulent-wedding-favors-for-your-guests-to-take-home-250x375.jpg 250w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/You-can-make-your-own-succulent-wedding-favors-for-your-guests-to-take-home-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/You-can-make-your-own-succulent-wedding-favors-for-your-guests-to-take-home-500x750.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/You-can-make-your-own-succulent-wedding-favors-for-your-guests-to-take-home-585x878.jpg 585w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/You-can-make-your-own-succulent-wedding-favors-for-your-guests-to-take-home-600x900.jpg 600w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/You-can-make-your-own-succulent-wedding-favors-for-your-guests-to-take-home-700x1050.jpg 700w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/You-can-make-your-own-succulent-wedding-favors-for-your-guests-to-take-home.jpg 735w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 735px) 100vw, 735px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>You can do these as simple or complicated as you want, but they\u2019ll be loved either way.<\/p>\n<p>The simplest approach would be to simply tie a <a href=\"https:\/\/amzn.to\/2CSPKW2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">ribbon<\/a> or <a href=\"https:\/\/amzn.to\/2CRU1sW\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">piece of paper<\/a> around the nursery pot the succulents come in.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/whimsicalwonderlandweddings.com\/pretty-wedding-ideas-at-the-house-meadow\/\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"https:\/\/i.pinimg.com\/564x\/f9\/64\/be\/f964be2c9e815c72ed9d524741c28954.jpg\" alt=\"Succulents are so cute and a favorite of mine for a spring wedding favor. (Hint: they're also surprisingly affordable!)\" width=\"564\" height=\"847\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>Or, you can repot them in a <a href=\"https:\/\/mountaincrestgardens.com\/1-8-x-1-6-terracotta-standard-clay-pot-w-drainage-hole\/?aff=2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">terracotta pot<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/mountaincrestgardens.com\/tin-pail-2-0-x-2-25-galvanized\/?aff=2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">tin pail<\/a> or <a href=\"https:\/\/mountaincrestgardens.com\/glass-votive-cups-multiple-styles\/?aff=2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">glass votive<\/a>. The <a href=\"https:\/\/mountaincrestgardens.com\/1-8-x-1-6-terracotta-standard-clay-pot-w-drainage-hole\/?aff=2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">terracotta pots<\/a> are my recommendation as this is a better long term home for the succulents.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-21838 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-wedding-guests-loved-these-succulent-centerpieces.jpg\" alt=\"The wedding guests loved these succulent centerpieces!\" width=\"1103\" height=\"735\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-wedding-guests-loved-these-succulent-centerpieces-80x53.jpg 80w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-wedding-guests-loved-these-succulent-centerpieces-200x133.jpg 200w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-wedding-guests-loved-these-succulent-centerpieces-250x167.jpg 250w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-wedding-guests-loved-these-succulent-centerpieces-400x267.jpg 400w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-wedding-guests-loved-these-succulent-centerpieces-500x333.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-wedding-guests-loved-these-succulent-centerpieces-585x390.jpg 585w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-wedding-guests-loved-these-succulent-centerpieces-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-wedding-guests-loved-these-succulent-centerpieces-700x466.jpg 700w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-wedding-guests-loved-these-succulent-centerpieces-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-wedding-guests-loved-these-succulent-centerpieces-800x533.jpg 800w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/The-wedding-guests-loved-these-succulent-centerpieces.jpg 1103w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1103px) 100vw, 1103px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>We also included <a href=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/product\/succulent-care-card-digital\/\">printed care cards<\/a> for each guest so they would know how to keep their new addition alive. You can purchase the files to print these yourself by <a href=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/product\/succulent-care-card-digital\/\">clicking here<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p>My two favorite places to purchase succulents and pots for wedding favors are <a href=\"https:\/\/mountaincrestgardens.com\/diy-succulent-favors\/?aff=2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">Mountain Crest Gardens<\/a> and <a href=\"https:\/\/thesucculentsource.com\/collections\/succulent-wedding-favors\/?aff=20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">The Succulent Source<\/a>. Both offer different color options and a few choices for <a href=\"https:\/\/mountaincrestgardens.com\/1-8-x-1-6-terracotta-standard-clay-pot-w-drainage-hole\/?aff=2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">pots<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/mountaincrestgardens.com\/tin-pail-2-0-x-2-25-galvanized\/?aff=2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">pails<\/a> or <a href=\"https:\/\/mountaincrestgardens.com\/glass-votive-cups-multiple-styles\/?aff=2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">votives<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/mountaincrestgardens.com\/?aff=2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">Mountain Crest Gardens<\/a> was kind enough to provide the succulents and terracotta pots for my sister-in-law\u2019s wedding and they turned out great!<\/p>\n<p>If you go this route, you will need to repot each of the plants into the fancier pot or pail you purchased. While not difficult, this is a time consuming process. We did 200 favors for the wedding. A friend and I sat together for 3 hours and got them all put together.<\/p>\n<p>You will likely want to have some extra <a href=\"https:\/\/www.bonsaijack.com\/category\/premixed-bonsai-soil\/succulent-soil\/?utm_source=succulentsandsunshine.com&utm_medium=referral\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">succulent soil<\/a> on hand, as not all of the pots were completely filled with soil (very normal). You may also consider adding a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.bonsaijack.com\/category\/bonsai-accessories-supplies\/succulent-top-dressings\/?utm_source=succulentsandsunshine.com&utm_medium=referral\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">top dressing<\/a> to hide the soil too.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-21827 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Give-your-guests-something-theyll-love-with-DIY-succulent-wedding-favors.jpg\" alt=\"Give your guests something they'll love with DIY succulent wedding favors\" width=\"1103\" height=\"735\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Give-your-guests-something-theyll-love-with-DIY-succulent-wedding-favors-80x53.jpg 80w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Give-your-guests-something-theyll-love-with-DIY-succulent-wedding-favors-200x133.jpg 200w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Give-your-guests-something-theyll-love-with-DIY-succulent-wedding-favors-250x167.jpg 250w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Give-your-guests-something-theyll-love-with-DIY-succulent-wedding-favors-400x267.jpg 400w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Give-your-guests-something-theyll-love-with-DIY-succulent-wedding-favors-500x333.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Give-your-guests-something-theyll-love-with-DIY-succulent-wedding-favors-585x390.jpg 585w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Give-your-guests-something-theyll-love-with-DIY-succulent-wedding-favors-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Give-your-guests-something-theyll-love-with-DIY-succulent-wedding-favors-700x466.jpg 700w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Give-your-guests-something-theyll-love-with-DIY-succulent-wedding-favors-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Give-your-guests-something-theyll-love-with-DIY-succulent-wedding-favors-800x533.jpg 800w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Give-your-guests-something-theyll-love-with-DIY-succulent-wedding-favors.jpg 1103w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1103px) 100vw, 1103px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>I\u2019d recommend putting these together the week of the wedding. While you can get them further in advance, you\u2019ll need to care for the succulents, make sure they get enough light, and ensure no one runs off with any before the big day \ud83d\ude42<\/p>\n<p>A week is enough time to get them done, but doesn\u2019t require you to dedicate an area of your home to care for them for weeks until the wedding.<\/p>\n<p>You can easily dress up the pots with a <a href=\"https:\/\/amzn.to\/2yMraSu\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">ribbon<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/amzn.to\/2q1TQD3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">paint<\/a>, or other decor of your choice. This will take more time together, but it\u2019s a great way to incorporate the wedding theme.<\/p>\n<p>Check out <a href=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wedding-favors\/\">this post<\/a> for more tutorials and ideas for succulent wedding favors.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-clearfix\"><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div id=\"cake\"><div class=\"fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-8 nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 0px;border-color:#eae9e9;border-style:solid;\" ><div class=\"fusion-builder-row fusion-row\"><div class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-7 fusion_builder_column_1_1 1_1 fusion-one-full fusion-column-first fusion-column-last\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-flex-column-wrapper-legacy\" style=\"background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;\"><div class=\"fusion-menu-anchor\" id=\"cake\"><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-8\"><h3>Succulent Wedding Cake Topper<\/h3>\n<p>You can really go crazy with succulents on your wedding cake. The wedding cake is often a huge highlight at the wedding so it only makes sense that you\u2019d use succulents on the cake.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_22128\" style=\"width: 610px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-22128\" class=\"wp-image-22128 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/stunning-succulent-wedding-cake.jpg\" alt=\"stunning succulent wedding cake\" width=\"600\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/stunning-succulent-wedding-cake-53x80.jpg 53w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/stunning-succulent-wedding-cake-200x300.jpg 200w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/stunning-succulent-wedding-cake-250x375.jpg 250w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/stunning-succulent-wedding-cake-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/stunning-succulent-wedding-cake-500x750.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/stunning-succulent-wedding-cake-585x878.jpg 585w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/stunning-succulent-wedding-cake.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><p id=\"caption-attachment-22128\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Image Source: <a href=\"http:\/\/weddingcolors.net\/lush-green-gold-wedding-inspiration-blue-valley-vineyard.html\" target=\"_blank\">Wedding Colors<\/a><\/p><\/div>\n<p>While real succulents are super fun, you can also have sugar succulents made! My friend Cassidy Harrison of <a href=\"http:\/\/flourandflourishcake.com\/\" target=\"_blank\">Flour and Flourish<\/a> creates amazing sugar flowers for wedding cakes and has done a few succulents.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-21842 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/This-succulent-stands-out-from-the-flowers-on-this-wedding-cake.jpg\" alt=\"This succulent stands out from the flowers on this wedding cake\" width=\"1103\" height=\"735\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/This-succulent-stands-out-from-the-flowers-on-this-wedding-cake-80x53.jpg 80w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/This-succulent-stands-out-from-the-flowers-on-this-wedding-cake-200x133.jpg 200w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/This-succulent-stands-out-from-the-flowers-on-this-wedding-cake-250x167.jpg 250w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/This-succulent-stands-out-from-the-flowers-on-this-wedding-cake-400x267.jpg 400w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/This-succulent-stands-out-from-the-flowers-on-this-wedding-cake-500x333.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/This-succulent-stands-out-from-the-flowers-on-this-wedding-cake-585x390.jpg 585w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/This-succulent-stands-out-from-the-flowers-on-this-wedding-cake-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/This-succulent-stands-out-from-the-flowers-on-this-wedding-cake-700x466.jpg 700w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/This-succulent-stands-out-from-the-flowers-on-this-wedding-cake-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/This-succulent-stands-out-from-the-flowers-on-this-wedding-cake-800x533.jpg 800w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/This-succulent-stands-out-from-the-flowers-on-this-wedding-cake.jpg 1103w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1103px) 100vw, 1103px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>My sister-in-law opted for a very simple cake and we did just a couple of succulents with it. I still love how it turned out!<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-21847 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/A-beautiful-green-succulent-on-the-wedding-cake-looked-simple-but-elegant.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1103\" height=\"735\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/A-beautiful-green-succulent-on-the-wedding-cake-lo