" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">Mountain Crest Gardens<\/a> or <a href=\"https:\/\/thesucculentsource.com\/collections\/succulent-cuttings\/?aff=20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">The Succulent Source<\/a> are perfect for cake toppers.<\/p>\n<div style=\"width: 544px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img src=\"https:\/\/i.pinimg.com\/564x\/71\/49\/f1\/7149f1a7fb98a10c1f9aae7970ef2c0f.jpg\" alt=\"a simple naked cake topped with succulents and greenery.\" width=\"534\" height=\"800\" \/><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Image Source: <a href=\"http:\/\/jennycookies.com\/2015\/05\/cactus-party\/\" target=\"_blank\">Jenny Cookies<\/a><\/p><\/div>\n<p>The succulents on the wedding cake can also be planted after they are removed to keep the memory of the wedding alive.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-21831 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Succulent-cake-decorations-made-the-desert-table-feel-relaxed-and-rustic.jpg\" alt=\"Succulent cake decorations made the desert table feel relaxed and rustic\" width=\"735\" height=\"1103\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Succulent-cake-decorations-made-the-desert-table-feel-relaxed-and-rustic-53x80.jpg 53w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Succulent-cake-decorations-made-the-desert-table-feel-relaxed-and-rustic-200x300.jpg 200w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Succulent-cake-decorations-made-the-desert-table-feel-relaxed-and-rustic-250x375.jpg 250w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Succulent-cake-decorations-made-the-desert-table-feel-relaxed-and-rustic-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Succulent-cake-decorations-made-the-desert-table-feel-relaxed-and-rustic-500x750.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\